705312f-b.title: Brooklyn: Kings Highway - 96th Street (East)
705312f-b.text:
King's Highway, (Hunterfly Road), at the N.W. corner of East 96th Street, showing the older John Mehl house and barns. This house does
not show in the 1929 1tlas of Brooklyn.
March 1925.
Eugene L. Armwruster Collection.
The same, looking west of 2ast 96th Street. King's Highway cuts
diagonally through the site of the Mehl house.
March 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
